# Minimal drift-isolation shot. One Trooper player, no extras, no
# input. Hold for 200 ticks. Pelvis should converge to a steady
# position with v ≈ 0 and stay there.

window 1280 720
seed   11 11
out    build/shots/m5_drift_isolate

loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Standard
spawn_at 640 984
mouse    1000 360

at 60 shot t60
at 120 shot t120
at 200 end
